      <hr><a name="skip_menu"></a><h1>563 - Binding Information (R)</h1>
      <hr>
      <div class="formatname">MARC 21 Bibliographic - Full</div>
      <div class="datename">October 2002</div>
      <hr>
      <table width="100%">
         <tr vAlign="top">
